<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification / Password Reset</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}</h1>
    <br>
    <p>We noticed a login to your account from a new device:</p>
    <p>- Device Name: <b>{{deviceName}}<b></p>
    <p>- IP Address: <b>{{ipAddress}}<b></p>
    <p>- Country: <b>{{country}}<b></p>
    <p>- Time: <b>{{time}}<b></p>
    <br>
    <p>If this wasn't you, we recommend updating your password immediately.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Regards,<br>Security Team</p>
</body>
</html>
